data.description: ***HUGE PRICE REDUCTION ****HONEY STOP THE CAR**** Welcome to this beautiful home situated in the heart of Riverside. Beautiful 2 story 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom Pool with spa home.  Well-maintained home inside and out, with laminated wood flooring and tile, Front and back yard well maintained, vinyl gate surrounding the home. Enough room for toys and RV parking, backyard with a patio is great for entertaining and enjoying the pool in the summertime. Close to the freeway and shopping. with also solar helps with those cost
